com.planet_ink.coffee_mud.Common.interfaces

Interface RoomnumberSet

  • All Superinterfaces:
    java.lang.Cloneable, CMCommon, CMObject, java.lang.Comparable<CMObject>
    All Known Implementing Classes:
    DefaultRoomnumberSet

    public interface RoomnumberSet
extends CMCommon
    A class for holding CoffeeMud-style room IDs of the form AreaName#[NUMBER], for instance, Midgaard#3001 This class is totally awesome because it stores them in an efficient way (holding room ids 5-10 not as 5,6,7,8,9,10, but as 5,10), but sorts them for quick reads. Stores the internal numbers using CMIntegerGrouper
    See Also:
    CMIntegerGrouper
